/-!
# Law-generated conormal first-order descent package

This file closes the G-07 theorem package on the fixed Boolean-circle
law-generated example.  It transports the kernel-section torsor through the
canonical `H⁰` comparison and through both first-order repair
representations, records choice independence and the primary effectivity
equivalence, and states the universal `H¹`-vanishing consequence.
-/

noncomputable section

